     FABHPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADHPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAKBPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FACHWP01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@JBN1  1
     C                     PARM           P@JBN2  2
     C                     PARM           P@JBN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@JBN4  1
     C                     PARM           P@UKYY  40
     C                     PARM           P@UKMM  20
     C                     PARM           P@UKDD  20
     C                     PARM           P@UBIN  20
     C                     PARM           P@CMAI  30
      *
     C           K@KKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN1
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN2
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN3
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN4
     C                     KFLD           K@UKYY
     C                     KFLD           K@UKMM
     C                     KFLD           K@UKDD
     C                     KFLD           K@UBIN
     C                     MOVE P@JBN1    K@JBN1  1
     C                     MOVE P@JBN2    K@JBN2  2
     C                     MOVE P@JBN3    K@JBN3  2
     C                     MOVE P@JBN4    K@JBN4  1
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKYY    K@UKYY  40
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKMM    K@UKMM  20
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKDD    K@UKDD  20
     C                     Z-ADDP@UBIN    K@UBIN  20
      *
     C           K@KKEY    CHAINABHPL031             55
     C           *IN55     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADDM6CMAI    P@CMAI
     C                     GOTO @JUMP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           K@KKEY    CHAINADHPL031             55
     C           *IN55     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADDJ6CMAI    P@CMAI
     C                     GOTO @JUMP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           K@KKEY    CHAINAKBPL031             55
     C           *IN55     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADDL1CMAI    P@CMAI
     C                     GOTO @JUMP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           @JUMP     TAG
      *
     C           K@KKEY    CHAINACHWP011             55
     C           *IN55     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADDZ1CMAI    P@CMAI
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
